            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Jeremiah.28:1-29:32",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2028%3A1-29%3A32%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeremiah%20Condemns%20Hananiah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20in%20late%20summer%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20fifth%20month%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20The%20fifth%20month%20in%20the%20fourth%20year%20of%20Zedekiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%20occurred%20within%20the%20months%20of%20August%20and%20September%20593%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Also%20see%20note%20on%201%3A3.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20that%20same%20year%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20fourth%20year%20of%20the%20reign%20of%20Zedekiah%2C%20king%20of%20Judah%26%23x2014%3BHananiah%20son%20of%20Azzur%2C%20a%20prophet%20from%20Gibeon%2C%20addressed%20me%20publicly%20in%20the%20Temple%20while%20all%20the%20priests%20and%20people%20listened.%20He%20said%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20will%20remove%20the%20yoke%20of%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%20from%20your%20necks.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EWithin%20two%20years%20I%20will%20bring%20back%20all%20the%20Temple%20treasures%20that%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%20carried%20off%20to%20Babylon.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20bring%20back%20Jehoiachin%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJeconiah%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Jehoiachin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20son%20of%20Jehoiakim%2C%20king%20of%20Judah%2C%20and%20all%20the%20other%20captives%20that%20were%20taken%20to%20Babylon.%20I%20will%20surely%20break%20the%20yoke%20that%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%20has%20put%20on%20your%20necks.%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EJeremiah%20responded%20to%20Hananiah%20as%20they%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20all%20the%20priests%20and%20people%20at%20the%20Temple.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAmen!%20May%20your%20prophecies%20come%20true!%20I%20hope%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20does%20everything%20you%20say.%20I%20hope%20he%20does%20bring%20back%20from%20Babylon%20the%20treasures%20of%20this%20Temple%20and%20all%20the%20captives.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20listen%20now%20to%20the%20solemn%20words%20I%20speak%20to%20you%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20all%20these%20people.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20ancient%20prophets%20who%20preceded%20you%20and%20me%20spoke%20against%20many%20nations%2C%20always%20warning%20of%20war%2C%20disaster%2C%20and%20disease.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20a%20prophet%20who%20predicts%20peace%20must%20show%20he%20is%20right.%20Only%20when%20his%20predictions%20come%20true%20can%20we%20know%20that%20he%20is%20really%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Hananiah%20the%20prophet%20took%20the%20yoke%20off%20Jeremiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20neck%20and%20broke%20it%20in%20pieces.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20Hananiah%20said%20again%20to%20the%20crowd%20that%20had%20gathered%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BJust%20as%20this%20yoke%20has%20been%20broken%2C%20within%20two%20years%20I%20will%20break%20the%20yoke%20of%20oppression%20from%20all%20the%20nations%20now%20subject%20to%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%20of%20Babylon.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%20With%20that%2C%20Jeremiah%20left%20the%20Temple%20area.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_12%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ESoon%20after%20this%20confrontation%20with%20Hananiah%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20this%20message%20to%20Jeremiah%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_13%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20tell%20Hananiah%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20You%20have%20broken%20a%20wooden%20yoke%2C%20but%20you%20have%20replaced%20it%20with%20a%20yoke%20of%20iron.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_14%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20I%20have%20put%20a%20yoke%20of%20iron%20on%20the%20necks%20of%20all%20these%20nations%2C%20forcing%20them%20into%20slavery%20under%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%20of%20Babylon.%20I%20have%20put%20everything%2C%20even%20the%20wild%20animals%2C%20under%20his%20control.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Jeremiah%20the%20prophet%20said%20to%20Hananiah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BListen%2C%20Hananiah!%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20not%20sent%20you%2C%20but%20the%20people%20believe%20your%20lies.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_16%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20must%20die.%20Your%20life%20will%20end%20this%20very%20year%20because%20you%20have%20rebelled%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_28_17%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ETwo%20months%20later%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E28%3A17%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20seventh%20month%20of%20that%20same%20year.%3C%2Fem%3E%20See%2028%3A1%20and%20the%20note%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20prophet%20Hananiah%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_29_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Letter%20to%20the%20Exiles%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EJeremiah%20wrote%20a%20letter%20from%20Jerusalem%20to%20the%20elders%2C%20priests%2C%20prophets%2C%20and%20all%20the%20people%20who%20had%20been%20exiled%20to%20Babylon%20by%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_29_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20was%20after%20King%20Jehoiachin%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E29%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJeconiah%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Jehoiachin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20queen%20mother%2C%20the%20court%20officials%2C%20the%20other%20officials%20of%20Judah%2C%20and%20all%20the%20craftsmen%20and%20artisans%20had%20been%20deported%20from%20Jerusalem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_29_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20sent%20the%20letter%20with%20Elasah%20son%20of%20Shaphan%20and%20Gemariah